excluded_middle
----------------

l1: $ emp , ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) ⊢ ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) $ by ax []
l2: $ emp , ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) , a ⊢ a $ by ax []
l3: $ emp , ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) , a ⊢ a ∨ ¬ a $ by or_intro_l [l2]
l4: $ emp , ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) , a ⊢ ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) $ by ax []
l5: $ emp , ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) , a ⊢ bot $ by bot_intro [l3, l4]
l6: $ emp , ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) ⊢ ¬ a $ by neg_intro [l5]
l7: $ emp , ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) ⊢ a ∨ ¬ a $ by or_intro_r [l6]
l8: $ emp , ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) ⊢ ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) $ by ax []
l9: $ emp , ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) ⊢ bot $ by bot_intro [l7, l8]
l10: $ emp ⊢ ¬ ¬ (a ∨ ¬ a) $ by neg_intro [l9]
l11: $ emp ⊢ a ∨ ¬ a $ by dne [l10]
